<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome to AutoHub!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to AutoHub!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Welcome to AutoHub - your premier car rental service! We're thrilled to have you join our community.</p>
    <p>With AutoHub, you can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse our extensive fleet of vehicles</li>
      <li>Book rentals with ease</li>
      <li>Manage your bookings and payments</li>
      <li>Access 24/7 customer support</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Ready to get started? Explore our available vehicles and book your first rental today!</p>
    <a href="#" class="button">Browse Vehicles</a>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help.</p>
    <p>Happy driving!</p>
    <p>The AutoHub Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{date}} AutoHub. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to you as part of your AutoHub account registration.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>